  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-table se-l-default\" id=\"SE-18f7107e-094a-4dc6-b660-aaf77e5ada69\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-table se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"width: 40%;\">\n<div class=\"se-table-container\">\n<table class=\"se-table-content\" style=\"border-style:solid;border-width:2px 0px 0px 2px;border-color:#004e82;\">\n<tbody><tr class=\"se-tr\"><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 100.0%; height: 154.0px; border-style:solid;border-width:0px 2px 2px 0px;border-color:#004e82; background-color: #004e82;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7a112e30-7939-47ae-80d2-1815380ae2bf\" style=\"line-height:2.3;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-fae133bd-de90-411c-bdc8-d4c914e2efe4\" style=\"color:#ffffff;\">Event ;</span></p></div><div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-afe2049f-b450-4a07-9e38-e33fe2b9045a\" style=\"line-height:1.6;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-3286f441-c0be-42a4-979f-007cbda8611a\" style=\"color:#ffffff;\"><b>행사 홍보물의</b></span></p></div><div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-6cfa04d7-c908-4df3-8da3-bdc813eae48c\" style=\"line-height:1.6;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-b8eface8-3f0a-4ed9-aa57-31400848d8f6\" style=\"color:#ffffff;\"><b>모든 것 (연속기획)</b></span></p></div>\n</td></tr></tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-bb8a5f98-57c1-42b5-83c5-677b09100d4b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-643c6191-8171-4801-806d-48537f87b80a\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-8a2c4e94-9019-40f8-8f24-98dc2ba2e09e\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">​</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-468fc99a-45f4-4053-a7f4-a6de1412e336\" style=\"color:#007aa6;background-color:#ffffff;\">봄이 지나 여름이 다가오고 있습니다. 여름에는 실내든 실외든 행사가 이어지고 있습니다. 실내보다는 실외가 더 많은 준비물이 필요할 수 있습니다. 배너나 현수막만 하더라도 실내 배너보다는 실외 배너나 현수막이 더 크고 더 많이 주문될 수 있습니다. 또한 방역이나 경호, 안내요원만 하더라도 더 많은 비용이나 인원이 배정됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-ce0a5bec-f051-4370-ab8e-d366c127af1c\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-9d8cb4e4-21fd-4d26-8129-9a552e3c6b5a\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-fcadb131-af16-4d2c-9cab-e0af24a564f0\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-2c2b3740-2600-4860-88b3-34bb4fbf2b4d\" style=\"color:#007aa6;background-color:#ffffff;\">항상 고객의 마음으로 블로그를 작성하는 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-ac1d3ebc-7d51-40e7-a5ab-7f14a77ab474\" style=\"color:#007aa6;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>(주)파파스컴퍼니</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-9c7cb3c1-1cf6-4157-bce1-761c270d57ea\" style=\"color:#007aa6;background-color:#ffffff;\">이 되겠습니다. 감사합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-wrappingParagraph se-l-inner-left\" id=\"SE-ad3314bb-ab54-44d4-932d-ed190cac3b3c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-component-slot se-component-slot-float\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-f4aa0316-aba7-4203-9ed5-361556dcb4ba\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA1MjZfMTIx/MDAxNzQ4MjM3MDQ3NTM0.mkkTwsOsBz_hYgRbFM8uEUqdsMAYU0IG7OgykfJYyoUg.O0FozMzLKcJNFdJX3KhFmlbhjIHAuyXmZQe3xjz9zw4g.PNG/2.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1625\", \"originalHeight\" : \"982\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA1MjZfMTIx/MDAxNzQ4MjM3MDQ3NTM0.mkkTwsOsBz_hYgRbFM8uEUqdsMAYU0IG7OgykfJYyoUg.O0FozMzLKcJNFdJX3KhFmlbhjIHAuyXmZQe3xjz9zw4g.PNG/2.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component-slot\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b9b2c8ef-1963-4ccb-8734-ae3457b5872f\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-6922e07c-e5ad-430c-925f-3ec439d4479e\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>기본적인 준비물</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e89a3477-49a7-44a4-a005-e8b4b2263919\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-5f3a454d-97ae-4032-9b08-991e67256117\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">어떤 행사든 간에 주최 측의 기획과 진행 순서가 미리 잡혀야 합니다. 이 진행 순서와 장소 날짜 등을 ppt로 만들어서 클라이언트 측과 최종적으로 조율을 합니다. 이 조율이 끝나면 이 기획 안대로 순서대로 작업에 들어갑니다. 사전에 미리 조율되고 결정해야 하는 것은 다음과 같습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ea1009c9-4ad0-4ac7-9b5d-e2c3bf1a5685\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-9b1b1260-3288-4a26-b5b5-2db2a73a0593\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-dfc4d316-2c79-466a-880c-afc488d6be5e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-5be4fe7e-c868-4586-ae47-822af06262db\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>1. 행사 포스터, 초청장(안내장)</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0637f2a4-9bb1-46a6-84b4-e305f70ea00a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-6a8b9de5-f4c5-4b59-aa33-0fbb97194ebb\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>2. 안내 배너 및 현수막 : 실내/실외</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e8d62e9f-3d00-4b63-b94e-07ddf96b4648\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-e0683b60-2fb8-42f1-ac43-33b93ca0044d\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>3. 행사 티켓, 이벤트 쿠폰</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9a722b14-715c-4866-b3fa-e138bb08d069\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-7a510639-7265-4ebd-afcc-93d9f5eea431\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>4. 안내(진행) 팸플릿</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ed12509d-7671-4886-84bf-4aef404c9961\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-8db8d777-196d-4405-8564-d0cc6dc84aa2\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>5. 홍보 책자</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6066aab4-724c-416c-bebd-c01189235501\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-02674d06-90aa-409e-a523-447396590d9f\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>6. ppt 발표 문서</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ebd682b3-2477-4a2d-9d13-2f9da0d92892\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-310669f5-2f5a-4ec9-a4ca-23b3562cb23d\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>7. 이름표, 시상식 표창장, 상품권 등 이벤트 물품</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3043abef-cfeb-432e-b165-510fa41ef387\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-55a98169-e63c-4067-918b-48b927f13898\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>8. 안내 지역 폼 보드, 약도, 공간 설명도 및 기타</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-da7ce644-8ce8-436a-9c54-531b1fd61e59\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b5a0e821-1b2e-4b2c-9e1a-bd0e95af0f24\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-fc800609-5148-4ebc-b62f-5b564d3c9c8e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-ad53a2f6-1eb1-43c1-bb64-274168911a01\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>행사 포스터, 초청장(안내장)</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0322bd24-683e-4f36-8a46-d4672d24793c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-f3503083-2c07-497b-b285-ffada37b372c\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">행사 포스터는 거의 소량 디지털 인쇄로 제작됩니다. 주요 장소에 부착하거나 디지털 이미지로 전송하기 위해 제작된다면 소량 인쇄만 진행하는 경우가 대부분입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a732766e-57a8-4e64-9963-376ebb1bf791\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-a732766e-57a8-4e64-9963-376ebb1bf791\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA1MjZfNzEg/MDAxNzQ4MjQyNzA2MTA1.FMSTo7mNLXvdPd1UNkQ032y4k3iIL-joBHNftbLqJPog.LNBlvF-d2XFfyFPaNUhQ1EjI92bDNLkUL3dl4XwsM10g.PNG/%EC%8B%A0%EC%9D%BC%EC%84%B1%EB%82%A8_250210.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"2481\", \"originalHeight\" : \"3508\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA1MjZfNzEg/MDAxNzQ4MjQyNzA2MTA1.FMSTo7mNLXvdPd1UNkQ032y4k3iIL-joBHNftbLqJPog.LNBlvF-d2XFfyFPaNUhQ1EjI92bDNLkUL3dl4XwsM10g.PNG/%EC%8B%A0%EC%9D%BC%EC%84%B1%EB%82%A8_250210.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-cb9f25cf-eb70-460b-ad18-391cf1e53e4b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3ea3a079-dc47-4683-99af-07ef8da2f100\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-5c125a23-8dd4-447c-a998-3b1dc1c0651f\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">이미지 예시입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a1944ea9-a881-4a68-b132-c803c5a4bc7e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-a1944ea9-a881-4a68-b132-c803c5a4bc7e\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA1MjZfOTcg/MDAxNzQ4MjQyOTI3OTg1.i36izz5_7Eh7xmrOydPIjTsSZkjACfC0JSz4bC9W-Vcg.rhlJBIFPJrEZ1w67l0KjpDzfXnDaMRrug3suxLK145cg.PNG/KakaoTalk_20250221_172856029.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1182\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1772\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA1MjZfOTcg/MDAxNzQ4MjQyOTI3OTg1.i36izz5_7Eh7xmrOydPIjTsSZkjACfC0JSz4bC9W-Vcg.rhlJBIFPJrEZ1w67l0KjpDzfXnDaMRrug3suxLK145cg.PNG/KakaoTalk_20250221_172856029.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-81527527-8956-4f54-979d-375d524d2ab5\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8eaeaa76-577f-43de-93e8-109356b3ce8c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-9934e87c-bd0e-4262-b6df-339b3c9346dd\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-0a848a6d-2a1e-43dc-91fd-76aa385d1a0a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-14575513-7128-492f-85e1-25fc42a35900\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-efd8dc1e-3c0e-4510-bf10-a59fb8bd1399\" style=\"\">행사 포스터의 납기</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-fde0f304-0aa3-4db0-9bf3-80d9abb5d70b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-db3aa0c6-0b44-4553-ad72-b597cd013230\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-c870fcd3-6d3f-4206-8ae9-ea3263fd9494\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>행사 포스터의 납기는 단 하루입니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9089a131-7585-4bcc-9486-34c74232ab07\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-4fb3d997-0062-4385-ad1b-b38654c74024\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ac3f612b-e921-44f4-93a8-45133d586abb\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-d2d96ee2-d7ba-43fb-ac42-07b781dceb2d\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">(주)파파스컴퍼니은 행사의 급함을 잘 이해하고 있습니다. 포스터는 설치도 해야 하고 손볼 것이 많아 가장 빠르게 납품해야 하는 경우가 많습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-283b1df0-5d2b-4c8b-829c-528bb16cdbef\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-ca91e1fe-eb9c-4a49-8e22-b56036369780\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e054de21-1bcc-4e6f-bc77-ebb97467d517\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-d6b915ae-95d7-4c51-9aab-5b6905bf0ea4\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fdd5f5;\">행사 포스터는 주문과 동시에 익일 택배 배송을 기본으로 진행되고 상황에 따라 당일 출고도 가능하니 참고해 주시기 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ca5cbb85-f810-4f40-b3c4-2f1a01cbff6c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-38847785-0a26-4076-9081-f90d11301916\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6ac5b42c-268d-4acb-bda3-02e2c606584e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-6961ad77-d842-4047-9cb2-f48559a9e763\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>행사 현수막/배너</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-cb42bdfe-8efd-481f-b256-c71182691665\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-a81ef9fe-c44a-4095-9978-971571244b16\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">행사 배너나 현수막은 행사에서 가장 중요한 인쇄물 중 하나입니다. 요즘 같은 선거철 시기에는 홍보 현수막을 많이 보고 계실 거라 알고 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-615b9a22-f78f-434f-af3e-a1ffee16a986\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:590px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-615b9a22-f78f-434f-af3e-a1ffee16a986\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA1MjZfMjgw/MDAxNzQ4MjQ0NzkwMTk3.VjWSn610CO5jNTE_z08Vw3lRLpAVLxSWhQLtFKSTgrAg.TlSmK21gXt5ThmQvTwP6SSPsrYVJUiERZdGk7YT8sHwg.PNG/2.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"590\", \"originalHeight\" : \"443\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA1MjZfMjgw/MDAxNzQ4MjQ0NzkwMTk3.VjWSn610CO5jNTE_z08Vw3lRLpAVLxSWhQLtFKSTgrAg.TlSmK21gXt5ThmQvTwP6SSPsrYVJUiERZdGk7YT8sHwg.PNG/2.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-baf6a6ea-bab4-4a1f-8a56-09b0380405ba\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3e7bc802-0df0-4cf7-8069-1c3b88fecf89\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-c333fd89-d8fe-4f21-bb1f-f92cd451172a\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">다음 글에서는 행사용 현수막/배너에 대해 알아보겠습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-8fdb1083-55a5-498d-aead-332616aa4a56\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-3272213d-d034-4092-be67-93337aee82a4\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-ali